{"tid":2222362,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"放木板雪糕筒堵路 年輕售貨員判160小時社服令","createTime":"2020-09-29T04:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T05:39:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51204a9d5a2b347383e7630132bc45ce65de47c8","tid":2222362,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"去年12月9日晚上，有示威者在旺角洗衣街及山東街交界一帶堵路，警方其後驅散並拘捕多人。事後三名年輕男女被控阻街，其中一人早前認罪，今被判接受160小時社會服務令。餘下兩人則否認控罪，案件押後至11月17日預審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/BRBWDU3BABCFNPOVQ7DDOUKGJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2FBRBWDU3BABCFNPOVQ7DDOUKGJI%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=6df28ba8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200929%2FBRBWDU3BABCFNPOVQ7DDOUKGJI%2F&h=8552e277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200929/BRBWDU3BABCFNPOVQ7DDOUKGJI/</a>"},{"pid":"97cb050448886786e2085a5d7fe492831f5a1c6d","tid":2222362,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}